WEBVTT

00:00:00.060 --> 00:00:01.309
All right,

00:00:01.319 --> 00:00:04.249
I was praying and the Lord told me

00:00:04.259 --> 00:00:06.530
this. I don't know who this is for,

00:00:06.540 --> 00:00:08.450
but it's for somebody

00:00:08.460 --> 00:00:11.270
because I was praying

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:13.370
and the Lord told me, 'I want you

00:00:13.380 --> 00:00:15.530
to tell them what I told you about

00:00:15.540 --> 00:00:17.029
healing.'I

00:00:17.039 --> 00:00:18.950
said,

00:00:18.950 --> 00:00:18.960
'Okay,'so

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:22.070
here you go, whoever this is for.

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:27.230
I was talking to some people

00:00:27.230 --> 00:00:27.240
whose

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:29.330
husband goes to our

00:00:29.340 --> 00:00:31.310
church. I worked on the staff at Victory

00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:34.010
Church here in Oklahoma

00:00:34.020 --> 00:00:37.389
City for a long time.

00:00:37.399 --> 00:00:40.910
I

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:43.010
was talking to some more people there on

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:45.350
staff, and a woman's husband was suffering

00:00:45.350 --> 00:00:45.360
from

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:50.569
some severe arthritis—really bad.

00:00:52.739 --> 00:00:55.130
His name was Stanley, and he told me,

00:00:55.140 --> 00:00:57.830
'Hey, Brandon, how come not

00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:00.529
all Christians are healed when they pray,

00:01:00.539 --> 00:01:03.650
and we suffer so long with

00:01:03.650 --> 00:01:03.660
stuff?'It

00:01:03.660 --> 00:01:04.969
was

00:01:04.979 --> 00:01:07.310
kind of a

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:09.289
challenging question and I didn't

00:01:09.299 --> 00:01:11.750
really have the answer for it, so I

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:14.090
said, 'Well, I'll pray about it. I

00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:16.190
don't understand why people go through

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:18.109
what they go through, other than that we

00:01:18.119 --> 00:01:19.850
live in a fallen

00:01:19.850 --> 00:01:19.860
world.'I

00:01:19.860 --> 00:01:22.010
said, 'I'll pray about

00:01:22.010 --> 00:01:22.020
this.'I

00:01:22.020 --> 00:01:24.710
started interceding

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.630
for this. Well, it was not very long

00:01:26.630 --> 00:01:26.640
after;

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:28.550
I was sitting on the edge of my

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:30.109
bed getting ready for

00:01:30.119 --> 00:01:32.210
bed, and I just asked in my heart,

00:01:32.220 --> 00:01:34.789
'Lord, why are not all Christians healed

00:01:34.799 --> 00:01:37.969
like they should be? I would

00:01:37.979 --> 00:01:39.950
like to understand more; give me

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:41.390
revelation.'I

00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:45.410
went to bed, and all of a

00:01:45.410 --> 00:01:45.420
sudden—I

00:01:45.420 --> 00:01:48.230
can't explain it to you, it's very

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:50.030
similar to how I went there when he took me

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.249
to the

00:01:52.249 --> 00:01:52.259
Tribulation—I

00:01:52.259 --> 00:01:55.370
was taken out of my body

00:01:55.380 --> 00:01:57.350
and

00:01:57.360 --> 00:02:00.889
I was at the foot of the cross,

00:02:00.889 --> 00:02:00.899
at

00:02:00.899 --> 00:02:05.149
his crucifixion.

00:02:09.539 --> 00:02:13.190
He was tied to a whipping post.

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:16.190
There was a Roman soldier with all this

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:18.890
Roman garb on, standing on

00:02:18.900 --> 00:02:20.869
his left hand.

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:23.930
He was chained up with his

00:02:23.940 --> 00:02:26.150
hands just like this on a whipping post.

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:28.910
His

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:31.010
hands were chained up

00:02:31.020 --> 00:02:33.770
with rope, and his hands were up

00:02:33.780 --> 00:02:36.589
on that whipping post.

00:02:36.599 --> 00:02:38.990
I can tell you the temperature

00:02:38.990 --> 00:02:39.000
in

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:41.930
that area; there was

00:02:41.940 --> 00:02:44.630
a dirt floor there, and

00:02:44.630 --> 00:02:44.640
the whipping

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:47.270
post

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:49.910
was wood.

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:52.729
The temperature was about 85 degrees

00:02:52.739 --> 00:02:55.670
outside, maybe 80. I could tell you

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.949
because I could smell the

00:02:57.959 --> 00:03:01.130
livestock in

00:03:01.140 --> 00:03:03.830
this coliseum area. I don't know what it

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:05.809
was; I could see

00:03:05.819 --> 00:03:08.150
these people right here and they were

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:10.250
watching him.

00:03:10.260 --> 00:03:14.270
This other man on this side

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:16.729
was wearing a black outfit;

00:03:16.739 --> 00:03:19.309
he was a

00:03:19.319 --> 00:03:21.530
big man, probably 400 pounds.

00:03:21.540 --> 00:03:24.350
He was a massive man—he wasn't

00:03:24.360 --> 00:03:27.470
overweight, he was muscular

00:03:27.470 --> 00:03:27.480
and

00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:28.670
looked huge.

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:32.210
He took that cat-of-nine-tails, and

00:03:32.220 --> 00:03:34.850
this other one took this canine.

00:03:34.850 --> 00:03:34.860
Jesus'back—he

00:03:34.860 --> 00:03:40.190
was a young man.

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:42.350
You see all this

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:44.869
stuff on TV where he looks old,

00:03:44.869 --> 00:03:44.879
but

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:49.009
no, he was a young guy,

00:03:49.019 --> 00:03:53.089
30 or 33 years old. In

00:03:53.099 --> 00:03:54.770
your mind you're thinking he's

00:03:54.780 --> 00:03:56.930
old because of pictures, but no, he was young.

00:03:56.940 --> 00:04:00.229
His back

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:04.250
had oily skin; he had dirt on him

00:04:04.260 --> 00:04:06.229
from the

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:08.690
sweat, and

00:04:08.700 --> 00:04:10.910
you could see the dirt on his back. He was dirty, and it was

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:14.149
oily,

00:04:14.149 --> 00:04:14.159
olive-looking

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:17.210
skin. Then they took

00:04:17.220 --> 00:04:21.289
though

00:04:21.289 --> 00:04:21.299
cat-of-nine-tails

00:04:21.299 --> 00:04:24.230
and they whipped him one time with it on

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:26.510
this side, and then this one whipped him

00:04:26.520 --> 00:04:31.550
on this side, and he screamed out in

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:34.129
agony. I watched it and I started

00:04:34.139 --> 00:04:37.189
screaming and yelling, 'Stop

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:39.530
this! Stop this!'but nobody could hear me.

00:04:39.540 --> 00:04:43.189
But Jesus was watching—Jesus himself

00:04:43.189 --> 00:04:43.199
was

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:45.650
with me. I was standing outside

00:04:45.660 --> 00:04:46.730
of my body; I don't know how this

00:04:46.740 --> 00:04:48.950
happened, but Jesus was standing

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:53.570
right here by me and he

00:04:53.570 --> 00:04:53.580
was

00:04:53.580 --> 00:04:56.270
watching himself be crucified.

00:04:56.280 --> 00:04:59.450
One man was whipping

00:04:59.450 --> 00:04:59.460
him,

00:04:59.460 --> 00:05:02.689
and Jesus's face looked up at

00:05:02.699 --> 00:05:05.629
them and he said (I'm going to do this

00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:06.830
without crying),

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:09.050
'I love you.

00:05:17.100 --> 00:05:19.189
I love you. I love you.'And he kept telling

00:05:19.189 --> 00:05:19.199
them

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:21.530
that every single time.

00:05:21.540 --> 00:05:24.710
They were mocking him

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:27.050
and they grabbed a hold of his beard,

00:05:27.060 --> 00:05:29.150
and I saw them rip huge

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:32.890
chunks of his beard out of his face.

00:05:32.900 --> 00:05:37.189
They kept going at it, and it was almost

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:40.249
like they were having fun; it was sick.

00:05:40.259 --> 00:05:44.500
They took those whips

00:05:46.139 --> 00:05:48.170
and they were just beating his flesh

00:05:48.180 --> 00:05:50.270
with it and it was tearing him

00:05:50.280 --> 00:05:52.969
to pieces. He had chunks

00:05:52.979 --> 00:05:55.189
of flesh hanging down off of his body

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:58.310
and it was just dangling down. It

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:00.110
was the most grotesque thing I've ever

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:04.189
seen in my life and blood was everywhere.

00:06:04.199 --> 00:06:07.010
And he looked at me—this Jesus, when he

00:06:07.020 --> 00:06:08.330
was standing right here—he looked at me

00:06:08.340 --> 00:06:10.189
and he said,

00:06:10.199 --> 00:06:15.730
'Brandon,

00:06:15.740 --> 00:06:18.830
what

00:06:18.830 --> 00:06:18.840
more?'No,

00:06:18.840 --> 00:06:21.710
he said this to me—I want to quote

00:06:21.720 --> 00:06:27.290
it exactly the way he said it—he said,

00:06:27.300 --> 00:06:31.670
'If somebody was to ask you

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:34.309
and challenge you about your faith,

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:36.350
saying that you're saved,

00:06:36.360 --> 00:06:38.029
and they said, "We don't really believe

00:06:38.039 --> 00:06:40.070
you're saved; you're not going to go to

00:06:40.070 --> 00:06:40.080
heaven,"you

00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:43.550
would fight them with

00:06:43.560 --> 00:06:46.070
every single thing. "Yes, I believe I'm

00:06:46.070 --> 00:06:46.080
saved!"You

00:06:46.080 --> 00:06:47.689
would argue with

00:06:47.699 --> 00:06:49.490
them; you would go after them.'That is what he

00:06:49.500 --> 00:06:52.010
said. I said, 'Yes, that's

00:06:52.010 --> 00:06:52.020
right,'because

00:06:52.020 --> 00:06:53.210
I don't question that at

00:06:53.220 --> 00:06:55.550
all in my heart.

00:06:55.560 --> 00:06:57.850
He said,

00:06:57.860 --> 00:07:01.730
'Healing is no different than your

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:05.150
salvation. I took your sin on my

00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:08.090
body and I took your

00:07:08.090 --> 00:07:08.100
sickness.'And

00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:11.469
he said, 'What do you not understand?

00:07:11.479 --> 00:07:15.730
By my stripes

00:07:15.740 --> 00:07:19.029
you are healed.

00:07:19.039 --> 00:07:21.850
By my stripes

00:07:21.860 --> 00:07:26.210
you are healed.'And he said, 'When you

00:07:26.220 --> 00:07:30.170
believe in my healing power as much as

00:07:30.180 --> 00:07:33.170
you believe in my salvation, then

00:07:33.180 --> 00:07:39.170
the manifestation will come.

00:07:39.180 --> 00:07:41.990
You've got to believe it that strong.'That is

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:43.909
what he was telling me.

00:07:43.919 --> 00:07:46.790
'Believe in what I did for you.

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:52.550
What more do you need? I took it

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:56.270
all on my body for you. I took sickness; I

00:07:56.280 --> 00:07:58.790
took disease for you.

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:00.650
I took it on me;

00:08:00.660 --> 00:08:03.890
by my stripes you're healed.'I saw

00:08:03.900 --> 00:08:05.150
his stripes.

00:08:05.160 --> 00:08:07.309
I saw him. I could hear the people

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:09.710
yelling in the background,

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:13.309
'Crucify him! Crucify him!'and he was

00:08:13.319 --> 00:08:16.670
beaten to a pulp for us

00:08:16.680 --> 00:08:18.469
so that we don't have to have sickness

00:08:18.479 --> 00:08:20.990
in our bodies, so we don't have to suffer

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:22.490
with it.

00:08:22.500 --> 00:08:27.050
By his stripes you are healed. And I saw

00:08:27.060 --> 00:08:28.070
it.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:30.950
He was beaten and he was bruised for our

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:33.529
iniquities; the chastisement of our peace

00:08:33.539 --> 00:08:34.790
was upon him,

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:40.070
and with his stripes you are healed.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:42.649
Believe it as much as you believe in

00:08:42.659 --> 00:08:44.269
your salvation.

00:08:44.279 --> 00:08:46.610
If anybody was to talk to you, try to

00:08:46.620 --> 00:08:48.050
talk you out of it, saying, 'You're not

00:08:48.050 --> 00:08:48.060
saved,'the

00:08:48.060 --> 00:08:49.790
same way

00:08:49.800 --> 00:08:51.650
you're

00:08:51.650 --> 00:08:51.660
healed—if

00:08:51.660 --> 00:08:53.990
anybody should try to tell you you're

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:57.350
not healed, you would tell them, 'No, I'm

00:08:57.350 --> 00:08:57.360
healed.'And

00:08:57.360 --> 00:08:59.030
you've got to believe it that much

00:08:59.040 --> 00:09:01.190
inside of you. You cannot doubt in your

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:04.190
heart; don't doubt your heart. Believe it

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:07.610
with all your might; believe it like you

00:09:07.620 --> 00:09:09.650
believe in your salvation. It's so much

00:09:09.660 --> 00:09:12.350
more. We have all those sins—we just

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:15.070
take it

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:18.829
for granted that we

00:09:18.829 --> 00:09:18.839
are

00:09:18.839 --> 00:09:22.430
saved, whenever all the

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:24.290
things they used to do to forgive sins,

00:09:24.300 --> 00:09:25.790
to atone for

00:09:25.790 --> 00:09:25.800
sins—killing

00:09:25.800 --> 00:09:28.790
animals, goats, and calves, and all

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:30.350
the stuff they did to wash the

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:33.230
sins away of the people...

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:35.210
we just go to him and ask him for

00:09:35.220 --> 00:09:37.610
forgiveness, and he said he's faithful

00:09:37.620 --> 00:09:39.170
and just to forgive us and cleanse us

00:09:39.180 --> 00:09:41.090
from all unrighteousness. But we just

00:09:41.100 --> 00:09:43.070
believe that, and it's simple. We just

00:09:43.080 --> 00:09:45.410
believe God: "You saved me, You

00:09:45.410 --> 00:09:45.420
washed

00:09:45.420 --> 00:09:48.350
my sins away."But the same faith it

00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:50.870
took to do that—which we realize how

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:52.730
much it probably was to wash all those

00:09:52.740 --> 00:09:55.850
things away—it took a sacrifice of

00:09:55.860 --> 00:10:00.290
Jesus. He took our sickness in His body;

00:10:00.300 --> 00:10:02.509
then He took our poverty. He said He

00:10:02.519 --> 00:10:05.630
became poor that we might be rich; He

00:10:05.640 --> 00:10:09.650
became sick; He became all these things.

00:10:09.660 --> 00:10:12.769
Look at it, just believe it, and He said,

00:10:12.779 --> 00:10:15.530
"Believe it with all your heart,

00:10:15.530 --> 00:10:15.540
Brandon."I

00:10:15.540 --> 00:10:17.750
don't know who that's for,

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:21.290
but I had that, and I came back.

00:10:21.300 --> 00:10:24.230
When I got back and I woke up the next

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:25.910
day,

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:28.430
I cried and cried

00:10:33.660 --> 00:10:38.269
because

00:10:39.540 --> 00:10:42.170
it was horrific what He went through.

00:10:42.180 --> 00:10:44.750
So Jesus did that for you.

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:47.810
Jesus died for you, and He loves you so

00:10:47.820 --> 00:10:48.530
much.

00:10:48.540 --> 00:10:51.050
I saw those people whipping Him, and He

00:10:51.060 --> 00:10:53.389
kept telling them, "I love you,

00:10:53.399 --> 00:10:55.910
I love you."When most people would just

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:57.350
want to spit on those other

00:10:57.350 --> 00:10:57.360
people—they

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:58.730
were spitting on Him, they were doing all

00:10:58.740 --> 00:11:01.130
bad things, shoving that crown

00:11:01.130 --> 00:11:01.140
of

00:11:01.140 --> 00:11:03.290
thorns on

00:11:03.290 --> 00:11:03.300
His head—and

00:11:03.300 --> 00:11:06.590
He just kept saying, "I love

00:11:06.590 --> 00:11:06.600
you."And

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:09.470
I just want to tell everybody: Jesus

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:12.290
really does love you,

00:11:12.300 --> 00:11:14.990
and He doesn't want you to suffer. He

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:17.090
wants you to be blessed.

00:11:17.100 --> 00:11:19.430
Beloved, I wish above all things that you

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:22.190
prosper and be in health even as your

00:11:22.190 --> 00:11:22.200
soul

00:11:22.200 --> 00:11:24.470
prospers.

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:26.810
So I want you to have a blessed day.

00:11:26.820 --> 00:11:28.670
Father, we just thank You, Lord, for these

00:11:28.680 --> 00:11:30.590
people right now. We just pray healing

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:33.050
over their bodies, and we thank You,

00:11:33.060 --> 00:11:36.470
Father, for a turnaround in their

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:40.069
circumstances right now. In Jesus'name, we

00:11:40.079 --> 00:11:42.889
pronounce healing and wholeness and

00:11:42.899 --> 00:11:46.190
wellness over their bodies. And we thank

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:48.290
You, Lord, for Your healing power going

00:11:48.300 --> 00:11:51.889
through them in the name of Jesus.

00:11:51.899 --> 00:11:54.230
From the top of their head to the

00:11:54.230 --> 00:11:54.240
soles

00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:57.350
of their feet, they are healed by the

00:11:57.360 --> 00:12:00.590
stripes of Jesus. And we take authority

00:12:00.600 --> 00:12:03.949
over sickness and disease. We take

00:12:03.959 --> 00:12:06.829
authority over poverty. We take authority

00:12:06.839 --> 00:12:09.170
over lack, not enough, and barely getting

00:12:09.180 --> 00:12:12.410
by. We take authority over it and we say

00:12:12.420 --> 00:12:15.350
it's under our feet in the name of Jesus.

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:18.230
And we thank You, Lord, for Your healing

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:21.110
power that delivers us from all sickness,

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:24.710
all disease in the name of Jesus Christ.

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:27.650
And we call you whole and healed and

00:12:27.660 --> 00:12:29.690
well in

00:12:29.690 --> 00:12:29.700
Jesus'name.

00:12:29.700 --> 00:12:32.030
Now

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:35.569
comment down below if there's a witness

00:12:35.579 --> 00:12:37.850
with you, if you're that person

00:12:37.860 --> 00:12:40.550
that I was talking to, because I really

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:42.230
believe the Lord wanted me to tell you.

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:46.430
And I hope my words gave what He

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:49.310
did for us a little justice, because

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:52.970
I know it's all so short of it. In my

